author: The Canadian Press
title: What is an essential service in the coronavirus crisis? Here is what will stay open in Ontario
description: As of 11:59 p.m. ET tonight, only businesses deemed essential workplaces will be allowed to remain open in Ontario during the COVID-19 crisis
content:
TORONTO — As of 11:59 p.m. ET on Tuesday, only businesses deemed essential workplaces will be allowed to remain open in Ontario during the COVID-19 crisis.
